Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.64,0:00:59.24,OP1-English,,0,0,0,,delirious with fever, i take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.35,0:01:05.32,OP1-English,,0,0,0,,if the dusty treasure map has been verified,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.65,0:01:11.19,OP1-English,,0,0,0,,it's not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.39,0:01:18.06,OP1-English,,0,0,0,,when it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.13,0:01:22.97,OP1-English,,0,0,0,,simply ride aboard someone else's biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.27,0:01:25.86,OP1-English,,0,0,0,,and pretend it isn't there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.81,0:01:31.70,OP1-English,,0,0,0,,we're going to gather up all our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.71,0:01:37.88,OP1-English,,0,0,0,,and set out in search of something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.22,0:01:41.12,OP1-English,,0,0,0,,a coin in my pocket,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.22,0:01:44.38,OP1-English,,0,0,0,,and do you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.86,0:01:51.03,OP1-English,,0,0,0,,we are!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:06.06,0:02:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What the hell... are you guys doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.69,0:02:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean? \NWe're here to get Nami.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:13.90,0:02:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. Where are Usopp and Johnny?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:16.41,0:02:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp! T-That's right!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:19.16,0:02:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no time to be loafing around here!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:22.03,0:02:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:23.45,0:02:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That bastard's been caught by Arlong!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:25.75,0:02:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta hurry before he's killed!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:27.75,0:02:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He {\i1}was{\i0} killed!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:28.96,0:02:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.13,0:02:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro Usopp is dead!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.21,0:02:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He was killed!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.72,0:02:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,By Big Sis Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.19,0:02:59.15,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,2000)\pos(352,110)}Everyone's Gathered!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.19,0:02:59.15,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,2000)\pos(352,458)}Usopp Speaks the \NTruth About Nami
Dialogue: 10,0:03:00.45,0:03:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.62,0:03:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's terrible!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.91,0:03:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She was a witch all along!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.04,0:03:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been winning Arlong's favor
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.21,0:03:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,so she could have the treasure buried \Nin Cocoyashi Village all to herself!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.38,0:03:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll calmly kill people for it, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.09,0:03:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,She's scum, rotten to the core!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.63,0:03:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,She had us all fooled the entire-
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.80,0:03:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.68,0:03:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Try saying that again! I'll kick your ass!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.34,0:03:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, Luffy. \NThis has nothing to do with Johnny.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.01,0:03:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't wanna believe me, then don't!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.48,0:03:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But I saw it with my own two eyes!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.35,0:03:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,She killed Big Bro Usopp-
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.06,0:03:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit spouting nonsense! \NNami would never kill Usopp!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.32,0:03:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We're friends!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.29,0:03:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But, I...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.20,0:03:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who're{\i0} friends, Luffy?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.74,0:03:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.16,0:03:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.82,0:03:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.20,0:03:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're our friend! We came to get you!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.50,0:03:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a big problem.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.79,0:03:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.92,0:03:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Friends? Don't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.76,0:04:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just a pathetic bunch of \Npeople cooperating with each other.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:00.97,0:04:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you! You killed him! \NI saw it with my own eyes!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.05,0:04:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare... \NHow dare you kill Big Bro Usopp?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.06,0:04:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So what? \NWhy not kill me as revenge, then?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.89,0:04:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.19,0:04:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you this much.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.44,0:04:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, Arlong wants to kill \NRoronoa Zoro and his men.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.86,0:04:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Because Zoro just had to be stupid.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.74,0:04:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how monstrously \Nstrong you guys are,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.74,0:04:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,you're no match for {\i1}real{\i0} monsters.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.66,0:04:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hang around this island, \Nyou {\i1}will{\i0} wind up being killed.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.33,0:04:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that it matters to me, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.42,0:04:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Her cool look is so enchanting, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.22,0:04:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}! It's me! \NDo you remember me?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.84,0:04:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's set sail together!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.64,0:04:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, you! \NYou're just complicating things!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.47,0:04:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Say what?! Love is always a hurricane!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.69,0:04:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Listen when people are talking!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.52,0:04:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Usopp?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.19,0:04:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Bottom of the ocean.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.52,0:05:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! Cut the crap!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.95,0:05:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,A swordsman would even \Nstrike a lady, Roronoa Zoro?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.45,0:05:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! You don't even know \Nwhat's going on here! Back off!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.66,0:05:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'd be irritated too, \Ncoming right off an insulting defeat.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.96,0:05:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.54,0:05:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Watch that mouth of yours!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.13,0:05:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind your own business, \Nyou damn bastard!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.30,0:05:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Bros! This is no time for \Nyou two to be going at it!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.44,0:05:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.92,0:05:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to fight, \Ncould you do it off the island?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.35,0:05:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't butt any more into this \Nland's affairs, you outsiders!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.01,0:05:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you still not get it?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.73,0:05:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The one and only reason I got \Nclose to you was for the money!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.40,0:05:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you're flat broke, \Nyou have no charm whatsoever!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.61,0:05:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have your ship back,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.91,0:05:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,so just go find a navigator somewhere \Nand go into the Grand Line!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.41,0:05:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Go look for your One Piece or whatever!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.00,0:05:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Just get the hell out of here! \NYou're an eyesore!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.29,0:06:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.05,0:06:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.60,0:06:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro Luffy?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.10,0:06:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to sleep.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.98,0:06:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Sleep?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.85,0:06:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,In this situation?! \NAnd right in the middle of the road?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.77,0:06:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't plan on leaving the island,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.61,0:06:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm not interested in \Nwhat's happening on the island.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.49,0:06:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm a little sleepy.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.54,0:06:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,– I'm going to sleep. \N– Huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.28,0:06:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Big Bro...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.92,0:06:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.21,0:06:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, whatever! \NGo ahead and die!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.43,0:06:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Na-
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.97,0:06:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Hurry!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.35,0:06:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the big deal?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.60,0:06:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Navy! The Navy's here!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.61,0:07:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Some survivors from Gosa \Nmanaged to contact the Government!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.32,0:07:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The Navy's come here to pick us up!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.03,0:07:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.78,0:07:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We're saved!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.62,0:07:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We can finally escape this island!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.33,0:07:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the infamous Arlong Park...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.58,0:07:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The world's on its last legs if pirates can settle down so blatantly.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.12,0:07:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, men!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.60,0:07:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Our mission today is to successfully extract from the island
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.55,0:07:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,the survivors of the town of Gosa,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.43,0:07:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,which was destroyed by the Arlong Pirates!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.98,0:07:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But I am left to wonder...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.52,0:07:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Would our brand of justice \Nallow us to overlook the castle
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.73,0:07:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,of this unchecked pirate?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.90,0:07:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It would not!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.65,0:07:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Our unit will now annihilate Arlong and his men!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.95,0:07:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare for battle at once!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.03,0:07:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.37,0:08:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Navy Branch #77?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.88,0:08:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. That's what it said.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.67,0:08:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,A newcomer.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.29,0:08:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone go there and negotiate \Nwith the head honcho.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.92,0:08:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If two million isn't enough
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.51,0:08:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,to keep them from trying \Nanything funny, get rid of 'em!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.72,0:08:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They're suddenly opening fire!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.15,0:08:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Arlong-{\i1}san{\i0}! Look out!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.57,0:08:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,H-He crunched a cannonball!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.36,0:08:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What terrifying jaws and teeth!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.37,0:08:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Arlong-{\i1}san{\i0}. The negotiations?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.75,0:08:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Canceled.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.42,0:08:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Let's go!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.67,0:08:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to fight!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.54,0:08:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be a Navy bloodbath!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.25,0:08:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Not so fast, guys.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.76,0:08:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to expend so much \Nenergy just to take out the trash.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.76,0:09:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll{\i0} go!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.64,0:09:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What foolish humans they are to pick \Na fight with us in these waters.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.31,0:09:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Three of our leaders'll make for a grand fight!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.82,0:09:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That ship won't last even three minutes!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.07,0:09:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's odd...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.28,0:09:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Commodore! \NThe cannonball appears to have been a dud!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.45,0:09:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire another! \NThis is a signal of open hostility!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.37,0:09:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We're dealing with Fishmen! \NDon't let your guard down, men!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.75,0:09:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.17,0:09:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been hit! \NIt's one of Arlong's men!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.00,0:09:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him! Commence attack!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.38,0:09:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Remain calm!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.76,0:09:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,One of Arlong's men, yes?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.72,0:09:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}I am Commodore Purinpurin of Navy Branch #77.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:42.72,0:09:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We are a somewhat well-known elite naval unit!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.60,0:09:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do not wish for death, \NI suggest you dutifully surrender-
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.19,0:09:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Commodore!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.21,0:09:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.53,0:09:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill him!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.03,0:09:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What's this shock?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.41,0:10:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me there's Fishmen under the ship?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.16,0:10:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to bother you like this,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.92,0:10:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,but we just took the liberty \Nof removing your ship's rudder.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:12.25,0:10:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,– W-What?! \N– Commodore! Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.22,0:10:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. \NI didn't hit any vital spots.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.18,0:10:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just hypothetical, Commodore,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.72,0:10:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,but if one were to move a large \Nreef directly into a strong current,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.69,0:10:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,what do you suppose would happen to the ocean?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.61,0:10:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.03,0:10:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Moving a reef?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.36,0:10:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't possibly be done!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.08,0:10:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Right around there, Hachi!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.99,0:10:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.70,0:10:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Commodore!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.32,0:10:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A giant whirlpool has suddenly appeared ahead!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:48.00,0:10:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The rudder's not working!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.37,0:10:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.25,0:10:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you. We removed the rudder.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.70,0:10:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This rudderless ship is now headed...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.97,0:10:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...into the depths of the sea.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.36,0:11:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This can't be happening...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.41,0:11:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This is reality.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.49,0:11:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way we can escape \Nfrom Arlong's control.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.06,0:11:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to make you work so hard!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.93,0:11:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all. \NWe know everything about these waters,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.27,0:11:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,from the winds to the depths. \NIt was a cinch.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.86,0:11:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,With our top skills, we have \Nno one to fear in these seas!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.79,0:12:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And let's not forget Nami's sea charts.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.49,0:12:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I moved the reef after checking that!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.95,0:12:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It even tells the flow of \Nthe currents and everything!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.33,0:12:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are some excellent charts, all right!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.75,0:12:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If we have Nami draw up charts \Nof all the world's oceans,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.41,0:12:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll be the eternal kings of the sea!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.63,0:12:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami's definitely vital to have for \Nthe creation of the Arlong Empire!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.97,0:12:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a real shame!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.09,0:12:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A shame?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.18,0:12:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He promised to let Nami \Nand Cocoyashi Village go
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.97,0:12:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,once she saves up 100 million berries.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.60,0:12:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,For reals, Arlong-{\i1}san{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.52,0:12:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really going to let Nami go?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.60,0:12:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,For reals, for reals?! That's a big waste!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.06,0:12:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.86,0:12:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what we agreed to eight years ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.10,0:12:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a man who'd die to keep \Nmy money-related promises.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.95,0:12:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Big Bro Zoro!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.79,0:12:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What on earth are you thinking?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.43,0:12:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Arlong is out to kill us!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.04,0:12:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So why aren't we running away?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.84,0:13:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that we know what Nami's really like,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.96,0:13:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,there should be no reason \Nat all to stay on this island!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.10,0:13:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,A reason for staying on this island? \NThere is one.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.34,0:13:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's{\i0} staying here.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.35,0:13:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell us you're still gonna try \Nto get her back too, Big Bro Zoro!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.35,0:13:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I have nothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.31,0:13:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He{\i0} decides who we have as navigator.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.86,0:13:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.40,0:13:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A-All right! Understood!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.91,0:13:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a short reunion, \Nbut our role as guides ends here!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.83,0:13:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Same for me! \NI don't wanna deliberately wind up killed!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.03,0:13:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Take care.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.80,0:13:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, until we meet again!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.00,0:13:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay well, you guys!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:43.76,0:13:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.16,0:14:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.36,0:14:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.08,0:14:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you suppose Nami-{\i1}san{\i0} was crying?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.12,0:14:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She was crying?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.25,0:14:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside her heart.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:23.30,0:14:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure they weren't tears \Nof grief for killing Usopp?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.97,0:14:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right. Are you serious?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.10,0:14:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you honestly believe \NNami-{\i1}san{\i0} killed Long-nose?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:46.36,0:14:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When she did that...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.15,0:14:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for my business!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.12,0:14:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This was my only choice!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.58,0:14:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When she did that,{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.87,0:15:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nami stabbed her own hand to \Nmake it look like she stabbed me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.13,0:15:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If Nami hadn't done that for me, \NArlong would've killed me for sure!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.14,0:15:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What now?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.32,0:15:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Manly Usopp can't just \Nturn tail after being saved!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.98,0:15:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For now, I gotta hurry and find Zoro!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.60,0:15:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is that... Zoro?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.61,0:15:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It is! Yes!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.64,0:15:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami didn't kill him. \NIs that what you're tryin' to say?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.74,0:15:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.70,0:15:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:32.87,0:15:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I did make her out to be a small fry \Nwho can't even watch a guy die.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.00,0:15:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She might've done it out of frustration.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.46,0:15:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Whadya mean, "small fry"?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.37,0:15:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so small about Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}'s chest?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.08,0:15:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all you can think-
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.17,0:15:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He's alive!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.89,0:15:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I think he's dead now...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.51,0:15:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.81,0:16:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Nami do this to you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.10,0:16:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. Me and him did that.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.15,0:16:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You{\i0} did it!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.98,0:16:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Luffy! You're here?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.65,0:16:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Just got here.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.07,0:16:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I came too! \NGood to work with you!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.28,0:16:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday I'm gonna kill you!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.20,0:16:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! You're pretty alright after all!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.41,0:16:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.28,0:16:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, we heard Nami killed you.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.70,0:16:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.41,0:16:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That damn Johnny! \NHe {\i1}was{\i0} talking nonsense after all!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.04,0:16:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No... In a way, it's {\i1}not{\i0} a lie...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:28.55,0:16:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's actually the opposite! Nami saved my life!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.99,0:16:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You really know how to trash a place.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.29,0:17:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Nami?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.65,0:17:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing. I'm just here to rest a little.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.75,0:17:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Breaking glass and furniture \Njust to rest is a bit much.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.01,0:17:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You have that treasure map open \Neven though nothing's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.30,0:17:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Something happened to make me mad, that's all!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.93,0:17:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Them, huh? Who are they?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.35,0:17:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You met them?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.49,0:17:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. \NSome Captain Something-or-Other.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.69,0:17:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He seemed kind of liar-ish, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.73,0:17:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear you smiled happily when \Nyou were traveling with them.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.70,0:17:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I haven't seen you like that in years.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.87,0:17:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk to me! Who are those guys?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.46,0:17:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We agreed you could tell me \Nanything, remember?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.26,0:18:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I had planned to forget about them...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.60,0:18:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I had erased them from my mind.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.77,0:18:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! I'm out!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.36,0:18:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it! \NYou win all by yourself again?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:15.69,0:18:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, hold on, Luffy! \NWhy do you have so many cards?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.95,0:18:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I get the feeling having more is better!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.24,0:18:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.24,0:18:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Learn the rules already!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.41,0:18:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Alright! Then let's say the one with the most wins!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.62,0:18:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}– Alright, it's decided!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.33,0:18:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,– But the more I tried to erase them, \Nthe more I remembered...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.83,0:18:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}– Quit deciding on your own!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.55,0:18:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, crap! We sprung a leak!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.01,0:18:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Stop it!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.30,0:18:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.39,0:18:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit thrashing around!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.23,0:18:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is, I once forgot the fate I bear for a short while...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.24,0:19:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you take your friends for?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.85,0:19:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I honestly felt like always being \Nwith them, if it were possible.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.11,0:19:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I see...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.08,0:19:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that'd hit you hard.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.24,0:19:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,To think that someone really showed up for her...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.71,0:19:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Friends, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.71,0:20:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The most painful word for her...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.43,0:20:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's how Nami pretended \Nto kill me and let me escape!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.27,0:20:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks to me like there's a reason \Nshe's in a Fishman pirate group!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.66,0:20:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.86,0:20:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what do we do? \NDo we storm Arlong Park?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.74,0:20:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hold on! We gotta find out what \Nthe story with Nami is first!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.03,0:20:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use, either way.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.54,0:20:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what you guys do, \NArlong's rule won't come to an end.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.04,0:20:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Nojiko!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.38,0:20:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's she?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.42,0:20:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami's big sister.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.54,0:20:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}'s older sister?! \NNo wonder she's so beautiful!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.26,0:20:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean it's no use?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.42,0:20:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, don't get any more \Ninvolved with this village.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.93,0:20:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave Nami alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.93,0:20:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll explain the circumstances.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.72,0:20:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Circumstances?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.89,0:20:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean why she joined Arlong's group?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.02,0:20:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. You'll feel like leaving \Nthe island once you hear it.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.73,0:21:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright. \NLet's hear this reason or whatever, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.86,0:21:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pass.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.82,0:21:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:04.65,0:21:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care about her past.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.12,0:21:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going, Luffy?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.41,0:21:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,For a walk.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.49,0:21:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A-A walk?! \NYou're not gonna listen to this?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.79,0:21:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I'll pass.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.50,0:21:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's he?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.50,0:21:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mind him. \NThat's just how he is.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.17,0:21:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll hear you out.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:22.13,0:21:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I don't think it's gonna change anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.55,0:21:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I'll listen, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.17,0:21:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna know what's happening on this island!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.52,0:21:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too! I want to know \Neverything about Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:36.39,0:21:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And now he's sleeping.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.69,0:21:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't sleep right after you say that!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.19,0:21:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. \N{\i1}This{\i0} is why Nami had such a hard time.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:47.82,0:21:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a Navy ship at the shore?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:50.53,0:21:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Branch #16's ship!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:52.58,0:21:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe Headquarters is taking action
Dialogue: 10,0:21:55.29,0:21:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,after what happened to Branch #77?!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:00.92,0:22:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Colonel Nezumi of Navy Branch #16!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.71,0:22:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring me Genzo, the representative of Cocoyashi Village!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:07.97,0:22:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Genzo, Colonel.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:10.68,0:22:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You, huh? Lead me to the \Nhouse of the girl named Nami.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:14.47,0:22:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami? But what on earth for?!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:19.90,0:22:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You simply need to lead the way.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:25.32,0:22:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It all goes back to eight years ago...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:32.95,0:22:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,To that day, when we were still little children...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:39.21,0:22:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,She was in this village.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:43.46,0:22:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Me and Nami will never forget \Nher as long as we live...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:48.51,0:22:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Her name was Bellemere.
