Dialogue: 10,0:24:11.34,0:24:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Bellemere! What a beautiful girl's name!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:14.26,0:24:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,How I'd love to meet her!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:15.60,0:24:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are Bellemeres yummy?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:17.18,0:24:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not food! \NIt's the person Nami-{\i1}san{\i0} will never forget!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:19.77,0:24:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Meaning she could be Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}'s... \NNami-{\i1}san{\i0}'s... Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}'s...!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:22.89,0:24:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! I can't sleep, Sanji!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:25.48,0:24:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you guys even serious \Nabout listening to Nojiko?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:27.69,0:24:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 10,0:24:28.94,0:24:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Untold Past! \NFemale Warrior Bellemere!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:31.53,0:24:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
